The US and the Soviet Union The US had nuclear weapons, which made that nation a superpower, so the USSR started to develop nuclear weapons to show superiority aswell, so being the other nation with a nuclear mass destruction weapon they became another superpower. So, after World War 2 tensions started to rise in between the two superpowers as one was a communist state (the USSR) and a capitalist state (the US) that is why the Cold War also started quickly right after ww2.
